		<description><![CDATA[After a 14-month hiatus, we dust off Just One More Book to participate in the Canadian National Day of Podcasting, a virtual event intended to bring stale shows out of retirement for one-day in a festival-like reunion of online content creators. In this episode, we highlight some of the chapter books we&#8217;ve read since parking [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>After a 14-month hiatus, we dust off Just One More Book to participate in the <a title="Canadian National Day of Podcasting" href="http://www.canadianpodcastbuffet.ca/?p=553" target="_blank">Canadian National Day of Podcasting</a>, a virtual event intended to bring stale shows out of retirement for one-day in a festival-like reunion of online content creators.</p>
<p>In this episode, we highlight some of the chapter books we&#8217;ve read since parking JOMB last year.</p>
<p>Andrea&#8217;s picks</p>
<ul>
<li><a title="Ribblestrop" href="http://www.andymulliganbooks.com/ribblestrop/" target="_blank">Ribblestrop</a> by <a title="Andy Mulligan" href="http://www.andymulliganbooks.com/" target="_blank">Andy Mulligan</a></li>
<li><a title="After Hamelin" href="http://site.annickpress.com/catalog/catalog.aspx?Title=after%20hamelin" target="_blank">After Hamelin</a> by Bill Richardson</li>
<li><a title="Elijah Buxton" href="http://www.scholastic.ca/titles/elijahofbuxton/" target="_blank">Elijah Buxton</a> by Christopher Paul Curtis</li>
</ul>
<p>Mark&#8217;s picks</p>
<ul>
<li><a title="Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy" href="http://www.douglasadams.com/creations/0345391802.html" target="_blank">The Hitchhiker&#8217;s Guide to the Galaxy</a> by <a title="Douglas Adams" href="http://www.douglasadams.com/" target="_blank">Douglas Adams</a></li>
<li><a title="Kendra Kandlestar and the Crack in Kazah" href="http://kendrakandlestar.wordpress.com/2010/10/11/whats-the-new-kendra-kandlestar-book-going-to-be-called/" target="_blank">Kendra Kandlestar and the Crack in Kazah</a> (the first draft of the next book in the series) by <a title="Lee Edward Fodi" href="http://leefodi.com" target="_blank">Lee Edward Fodi</a></li>
</ul>
<p><img class="alignnone" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4106/5192126523_aeb637b925_m.jpg" alt="" width="180" height="240" /> <img class="alignnone" src="http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4110/5192720496_cced46c595_m.jpg" alt="" width="180" height="240" /></p>
