			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignright" title="Bedtime Snack" src="http://www.justonemorebook.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/06/isaac_220.jpg" alt="" width="220" height="220" />We opened our <a style="text-decoration: none; color: #6c3bca;" title="Love of Reading gallery" href="http://www.justonemorebook.com/love-of-reading-gallery" target="_blank">Love of Reading Gallery</a> in July 2008 and invited all illustrators to submit original artwork that promotes a love of reading.  Submissions spanned the globe including Venezuela and Romania and covered all age ranges.</p>
