<li><a title="Of Curiosity and Creationism: One Beetle Too Many (The Extraordinary Adventures of Charles Darwin)" href="http://tinyurl.com/7zvgog">One Beetle Too Many â€” The Extraordinary Adventures of Charles Darwin</a></li>
<li><a title="Back to the Future: Neo Leo (the Ageless Ideas of Leonardo da Vinci)" href="http://www.justonemorebook.com/2009/08/07/back-to-the-future-neo-leo-the-ageless-ideas-of-leonardo-da-vinci/">Neo Leo (the Ageless Ideas of Leonardo da Vinci)</a></li>
<li><a title="Inventions, Adventure &amp; Conservation: The Fantastic Undersea Life of Jacques Cousteau" href="http://www.justonemorebook.com/2009/04/15/inventions-adventure-conservation-the-fantastic-undersea-life-of-jacques-cousteau/">The Fantastic Undersea Life of Jacques Cousteau</a></li>
<li><a title="The Value of Believing in Yourself: The Story of Louis Pasteur" href="http://www.justonemorebook.com/2006/09/13/the-value-of-believing-in-yourself-the-story-of-louis-pasteur/">The Value of Believing in Yourself: The Story of Louis Pasteur</a></li>
